<div class="container">
  <div class="titlebox col-md"> <!-- Title & sub-title, col-md = auto eq-col-width -->
    <h1>Job Opportunities</h1>
    <h3>This is a list of the most popular recruitment websites.</h3>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container"> 
  <div class="intro-text col-md"> <!-- "col-md" = auto equal-column-width -->
    In addition to these, you can also find job vacancies for a particular technology by typing its name into LinkedIn’s search box.
  </div>
  <div class="intro-text col-md">
    Networking is a good way to hear about job openings, which you can do at your language’s local user group or by helping out on group coding projects.
  </div>
  <br />
</div>

<!-- Section headings are stored in the 'Heading' database table. -->
<!-- The headings needed for this page have 'id' numbers from 11 to 16 -->
<% for this_heading in 11..16 %>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading col-md"> <!-- Sect. headings have their own CSS style -->
      <%= @headings.find(this_heading).heading_text %> <!-- Show section heading text for a particular id num -->
    </div>
    <ul>
      <div class="bullet-point col-md"> <!-- Show links as bullet points -->
        <% @links.where(heading_id: this_heading).each do |link| %> <!-- All links for this heading_id -->
          <li><b><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href='<%= link.URL %>'><%= link.title %></a></b></li>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </ul>
  </div>
<% end %>